scripted vs declarative pipeline

Both supports groovy

scripted				decleartive
1) syntax			pipeline {
	
node {					}

}

2)node and stage		pipeline,agent,stages,stage and step (manadatory blocks)

3)Legacy(old pipeline)			Declrative

4) job is completed-->build-->test-->deploy

5) If you want to rerun, replay (rerun it completely) option in scripted pipeline

6) Rerun the job in declarative pipeline--> replay and restart from stage option are available
	
